@token = paste-your-jwt-token-here
@claimId = paste-claim-id-here

### Submit a claim
POST http://localhost:5000/api/claims
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: BEARER {{token}}

{
  "itemId": "FOUND_ITEM_ID_HERE",
  "description": "This is my wallet, it has a blue leather cover with my initials on it",
  "uniqueDetails": "Has a small scratch on the back and contains a BUE student ID"
}

###

### Get claim details
GET http://localhost:5000/api/claims/{{claimId}}
Authorization: BEARER {{token}}

###

### Approve claim (finder only)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/claims/{{claimId}}/approve
Authorization: BEARER {{token}}

###

### Reject claim
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/claims/{{claimId}}/reject
Authorization: BEARER {{token}}

###

### Complete claim
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/claims/{{claimId}}/complete
Authorization: BEARER {{token}}
